Fashiolista.com is an exciting online fashion community with over 1.5 million users from all over the world. Our platform was launched in Spring 2010 and from our HQ <strong>in Amsterdam</strong> we work with a dedicated team to spread our love for fashion.</p>
<p>
Fashiolista is scouting for <strong>fashionable interns</strong> to support us with <strong>social media</strong>, <strong>branding</strong> and&nbsp;<strong>overall&nbsp;communication</strong>.</p>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>We are looking for someone who:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
loves Fashiolista.com</li>
<li>
eats, sleeps and breathes fashion</li>
<li>
reads fashion blogs</li>
<li>
radiates positive energy</li>
<li>
gets things done. Regardless.</li>
<li>
speaks &amp; writes English exceptionally well</li>
<li>
has a background in communication and/or branding</li>
</ul>
