<ul>
<li>
have a blog</li>
<li>
use Twitter, Facebook, Tumblr, Pinterest or Instagram</li>
<li>
love online fashion shopping</li>
<li>
speak Portuguese,&nbsp; Spanish or French</li>
<li>
are a native English speaker</li>
<li>
have good Photoshop and/or InDesign skills</li>
</ul>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>What will you be doing @ Fashiolista HQ?</strong><br />
You will help with PR, social media, community interaction and meet ups.&nbsp; You will communicate with fashion bloggers, update our Twitter, Facebook and other social media&nbsp; accounts. Social media is critical for us, so we take these things very seriously. You will help us in communicating with the Fashiolista community. You&rsquo;ll be receiving their feedback and will be answering their questions. You&rsquo;ll help us organize events and meet ups for fashion bloggers, industry experts and Fashiolista members from Amsterdam, all the way to London, Rio and NYC.</p>
<p>
<br />
You&rsquo;ll do a ton of other stuff that you (and we) can&rsquo;t even imagine right now. Consider that a perk of working for a young start-up company.</p>
<p>
This internship gives you the opportunity to do amazing things with a group of awesome people. Interested? Send us your application including r&eacute;sum&eacute;.</p>
